              "noDataMessage": "No multi-cluster storage latency metrics for the selected scope and time range. Confirm AMA + a DCR collecting `LogicalDisk(*)\\Avg. Disk sec/Read|Write` and `Cluster CSV File System(*)\\Avg. Disk sec/Read|Write` is deployed — expand the \"Show DCR Setup Guide\" section in the Capacity Overview tab for setup guidance.",
